summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of North & West Seventy-fourth Street from Winona Avenue to Eighty Avenue Northwest et al in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 21218, creating Local Improvement District No. 2124 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
